### Network of Táin Bó Cúailnge

Interactive network of the Irish epic the *Táin Bó Cúailnge*. 

Green edges are friendly interactions, red hostile. 
Blue nodes are male characters, red are female. Gender was not specified for grey nodes.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
